# ErrorBot – Hardware Connections

## ESP32 to L298N
- IN1 → GPIO 26  
- IN2 → GPIO 27  
- ENA → 5V (jumper enabled)  
- GND → GND  

> Only Channel A is used due to Channel B failure.

## OLED Display (I2C)
- VCC → 3.3V  
- GND → GND  
- SDA → GPIO 21  
- SCL → GPIO 22  

## Physical Safety Switch
- One terminal → GPIO 33  
- Other terminal → GND  
- Configured using INPUT_PULLUP  

## Power Supply
- ESP32 powered via USB  
- Motors powered using battery pack  
- Common ground maintained
